{{Infobox football club | clubname = Milerock | image = Milerock FC.svg | image_size = 200px | fullname = Milerock Football Club | nickname = ''Strikers'' | founded = 1972 | ground = | capacity = | chrtitle = President | chairman = | mgrtitle = Manager | manager = | league = [[GFF National Super League]] | season = [[2010 GFF National Super League|2010]] | position = 2nd | current = | website = }}
'''Milerock''' is a [[Guyana|Guyanese]] football club based in [[Linden, Guyana|Linden]], competing in the [[Guyana National Football League]], the top tier of Guyanese football. The club has a [[local derby|local rivalry]] with fellow Linden-based club, [[Bakewell Topp XX]].
