{{Infobox football biography |name = Panutche Camará |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = Panutche Amadu Pereira Camará<ref name = "SW"/> |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1997|2|28|df=y}}<ref name = "SW"/> |birth_place = [[Canchungo]], [[Guinea-Bissau]]<ref name = "SW"/> |height = {{height|m=1.85}}<ref name = "SW"/> |position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] |currentclub = [[Crawley Town F.C.|Crawley Town]] |clubnumber = 28 |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = [[Barnsley F.C.|Barnsley]] |years1 = 2017 |clubs1 = [[Dulwich Hamlet F.C.|Dulwich Hamlet]] |caps1 = 9 |goals1 = 4 |years2 = 2017– |clubs2 = [[Crawley Town F.C.|Crawley Town]] |caps2 = 47 |goals2 = 4 |club-update = 10:34, 26 November 2018 (UTC) }} '''Panutche Amadu Pereira Camará''' (born 28 February 1997) is a Bissau-Guinean professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for English {{English football updater|CrawleyT}} club [[Crawley Town F.C.|Crawley Town]], as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]].<ref name = "SW">{{soccerway|panutche-camara/476242|accessdate=11 June 2017}}</ref>
==Career== After playing for [[Barnsley F.C.|Barnsley]] and [[Dulwich Hamlet F.C.|Dulwich Hamlet]], Camará signed a two-year professional contract with [[Crawley Town F.C.|Crawley Town]] in June 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40204552|title=Panutche Camara: Crawley Town sign Dulwich Hamlet forward|date=8 June 2017|accessdate=11 June 2017|publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref> He scored his first goal for Crawley on his debut in a 5–1 [[EFL Cup]] defeat at [[Birmingham City]] on 8 August 2017.<ref name = "2017-18"/>
