The '''[[Philippines]]''' competed at the '''[[1988 Winter Olympics]]''' in [[Calgary]], [[Canada]]. The nation returned after a 16-year absence since they last competed at the [[1972 Winter Olympics]] in [[Sapporo]], [[Japan]].
